    a. Licensed Material is provided "as-is" without warranties.
    b. Licensor is not liable for any damages or losses.
    c. These provisions aim to be as close to an absolute waiver as permitted.

Section 6 – Term and Termination.

    a. Rights terminate automatically if You violate the license.
    b. They are reinstated:
           i.   automatically if cured within 30 days;
           ii.  by express reinstatement from the Licensor.
    c. Sections 1, 5, 6, 7, and 8 survive termination.

Section 7 – Other Terms and Conditions.

    a. Licensor is not bound by any additional terms unless agreed.
    b. Side agreements are separate.

Section 8 – Interpretation.

    a. This license does not restrict lawful uses without permission.
